Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,snapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, we'd all like to kill that rotten son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but Nagisa might just go through with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You have to stop—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be gettin' cocky, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the pitiful way you looked at me when that medicine got blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit worryin' about other people, ya damn wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This virus'll go away by itself with a good night's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Terasaka... You mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder is murder, even if it's a piece of trash like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna give in to the crazy and throw your chance at ten billion out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Terasaka-kun's right, Nagisa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing him isn't worth it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and being in a blind rage will only work against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he doesn't know anything about the remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ask the poisoner downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just knock him out. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, quit being a wet blanket!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't come at me with true killing intent, what's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this squirt's bloodlust for revenge in a most humiliating way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally my own shame will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa-kun, take Terasaka-kun's stun gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His life, or my life. His words, or Terasaka-kun's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Think carefully, now: which are more worthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Terasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You've got one hell of a fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you even make it here like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddup. You wanna look at somethin', look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him to within an inch of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, don't {\i1}you{\i0} look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Korosensei, Nagisa's put the stun gun away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're determined to use the knife. That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}do{\i0} have some spare vials of that remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come at me like you mean it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or if your pals get in our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can kiss these babies goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that, Karasuma? Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff takes a good month to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough for everyone, but it {\i1}is{\i0} your last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Karasuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you determine that Nagisa-kun's life is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't hesitate to shoot Takaoka-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For him to say that when he can usually see what's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This must be our most dangerous predicament yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I can tell that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may have managed to defeat those three assassins on our own terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now the tables are completely turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if Shiota Nagisa did try to turn this into an assassination...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Aren't you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takaoka's a whole different man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's in battle mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even with a mind gone mad, he's still an elite soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His impregnable defense will shut down any surprise attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The build!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Defeating him is far harder than scoring in first place in the national mock exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he can beat that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't go getting tired on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's time for me to pull out one of these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A traumatic image accompanies his knife in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When he caught me off-guard with that smile of his—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that's when everything went off the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will {\i0}not{\i1} make the same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut off your hands and feet and have them stuffed and mounted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep them with me and cherish them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Karasuma-sensei! You've got to shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we still leaving them to it, Terasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just about ready to join the fray myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You been skippin' practice, Karma, so you don't know, but Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still got somethin' up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the deadly technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't look like one, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in a tight spot as an assassin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I used this to squeeze my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it has conditions that must be met—three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First: you must have two weapons.{fucking kirito}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Second: you must be up against an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And third: your foe must know the terror of being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takaoka-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you be my guinea pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A deadly technique doesn't necessarily kill instantly.{deep}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the ideal conditions, of course, any assassin can do the deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But reality is rarely that agreeable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,especially when your target is a pro with an airtight defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This technique can reliably create an ideal killing situation in such a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It sets the stage for an instant kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sets the stage, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Move from a standstill, as fast as you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as you can, and make it as loud as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You... lousy... brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This works best when they're almost within range{ of the knife}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The closer you get, the more the target will focus on your knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gently let go of that knife in midair while their attention is on it, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What... just... happ—{he clapped in your face. whoa.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will not overlook those few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In one fluid motion, swiftly draw your second blade, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It... can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This brat... got me... again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish him off, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A good jolt to the neck'll knock him out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He taught me bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That some kinds of bloodlust are wrong to hold on to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and how important it is to have friends to pull you away from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pain of being hit, the fear of a real fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've learned so much from this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'd done terrible things, but setting that aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I ought to thank him for his lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I couldn't thank him without putting on a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, please... don't end this with that smile of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That face will haunt my nightmares until the day I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takaoka-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We beat the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{lunch time}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Nagisa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried about how things would turn out. I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm fine, but... now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The remedy we took from Takaoka-sensei won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start by getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've called a chopper, so you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring up the poisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. You're not gonna need no stinkin' remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You brats thought you could get out of here alive, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've defeated the man who hired you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no further reason to fight us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've mostly recovered, and these students are plenty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we stop now before anyone else gets hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't know when to give up—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, "okay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contracts don't cover avenging the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's like I said: you don't need any remedy.{called it}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This here's what I gave you:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a souped-up version of the common stomach bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll keep going strong for another three hours or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but then it'll rapidly lose its efficacy and become harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is what our boss {\i1}told{\i0} us to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had, you'd really be in dire straits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before using that virus, we three talked-eth it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our boss only gave-eth you one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We figured we could do the handover without having to resort-eth to a deadly virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was enough to make you {\i1}feel{\i0} like your lives were in danger, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you went against orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that when he's paying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think pros will do {\i1}anything{\i0} for money, you got another think comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best to abide by our client's wishes, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow this remedy up right before their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't wait to see their faces crushed with despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he never had any intention of giving you the remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So either we become the killers of a bunch of respectable junior-high kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or we take a hit to our professional standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We just calmly weighed up which option posed a greater risk to our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why, sorry to say, none of you will be dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the patients that supplement and put 'em to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like it says on the tin, they'll feel even better than before they were sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll believe it once I see those students home safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to detain you for a while for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:15:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well. You've got a week to wind it up before our next job starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not going-eth for a rematch, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you just thirsting for revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't kill-eth people out of spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for the day someone puts-eth a hit out on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better become-eth someone worth targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you have it, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want us to come kill you, you've gotta make it big first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll give you the pro assassin's grand tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The assassins were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}having left us with their own words of encouragement of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One buzz from Karasuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the signal that they've escaped.{pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wanna go down the mountain and see the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't someone drive me down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me! Me me me! Pick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so our big infiltration mission was completed with no one at the hotel the wiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Terasaka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for calling me out back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to make the wrong move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One less student'd make it that much harder to kill that octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We went back to our hotel, where everyone was waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and told them it was going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We slept like logs, each of us tired out in different ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and when we woke, it was evening on the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one crazy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad we got through it in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one in the most danger, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You do get into sticky spots now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We worry, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,20,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.50,Default,,0,0,20,,Or should I say "evening"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,20,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,20,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see everyone's in their P.E. gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the only guests, and these are nice and comfy.{i like shorts}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'd be cruel to have to think up a whole new day's worth of outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So Korosensei's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not like it's going to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's in there nice and tight so we can kill him when he reverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Karasuma-sensei has been leading the charge without rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He shows no signs of fatigue at all. Pretty amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is. I wonder if we'll be as awesome as him in ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch-sensei might not look like it, but she's great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So were the assassins we met at the hotel.{monhun pls go}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those moves mastered through long years of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{overlap}Go, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and their work ethic really inspired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{overlap}Gimme a max potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there are people like Takaoka who I really {\i1}don't{\i0} want to turn into.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We follow people we admire and leave behind the ones we reject.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing up is probably just doing that over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even as we asked that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we already knew the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You suffered so much on account of my cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you battled enemies and a virus—and did a fine job of it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Korosensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just not the same without your tentacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.76,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{overlap}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's enjoy the rest of our trip, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're going back tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With all the time I spent in my Absolute Defense Form, I've barely gotten to enjoy myself at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}you're{\i0} sure full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a one-time thing: summer camp with my students!
