Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't waste a single second!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said not to waste a single second, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah yes, Karma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait until your target lets down his—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought this might be our chance to do him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Want to take a shot, Nagisa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to make the most of the time we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{overlap}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{overlap}Over here!{switched order}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm feeling better and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You put on a swimsuit underneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme at 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm just going to swell right up, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what summer's all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.05,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bit on the small side, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, students, there'll be fireworks after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to play with me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That octopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Karasuma-san, should we start heading out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were busy burying him in concrete!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've invited me if you were heading to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What a swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Karasuma, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave these kids behind and check out that—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} a bitch.{this doesn't really work but w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You squirts have been giving some real cheek lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mess with me, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our E Class—the End Class—is the assassination classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are killers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and our target is our teacher.
